		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Sometimes parts heating up causes the part to fail, I've seen it with an Xbox before. And 360 of course with the old (RROD)
<br />
<br />
<br />Maybe cool some hardware that is used to read the controller and see if it helps, if it does, it needs replaced. If not, good luck!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


